{"title":"家里有了地  一个女人寄给丈夫的好音信","authors":["王芜"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里有了地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个女人寄给丈夫的好音信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王芜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄里开会分地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱得了六亩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父老说给咱们好地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先让军属自己挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑完了再给旁人分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子他爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今以后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不再过那掉顿的苦日子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属头等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说能多打下粮食好几斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——农会说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先给咱们家耕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送粪代耕早齐全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐的我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着咱孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天到咱的地里去看苗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看它出来没出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是有草长出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就拔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农会照顾真周到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送米送柴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水与代耕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子他爸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你放心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽有两个孩子坠我脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前后院里的空地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我全种上苞米和白菜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——已经下来小白菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我娘三个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃的甜又香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——吃穿都不愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也有地啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我决心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要当先！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不是共产党来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们千年万年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也捞不着一块土拉疙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于秦皇岛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}